casebody.data:
Frankie Jae LORDMASTER, fka Jason Robert Goldader, petitioner,
v.
DISTRICT COURT OF NORTH DAKOTA, CASS COUNTY. No. 15-8836. Supreme Court of the United States June 6, 2016.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
